{"tid":98096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美退出TPP 越南可能成為中美貿易戰受惠者","createTime":"2017-01-28T06:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T13:50:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05dbeb7ad6d78b862f99fb55e2375f06bb169c51","tid":98096,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:57:41.000Z","msg":"美退出TPP 越南可能成為中美貿易戰受惠者<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/5/2252730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F5%2F2252730&d=bSFqEsVV1KvOTMWKz21YWAv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=96ea5ad3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/5/2252730</a><br />\n<br />\n經濟日報 記者林筠╱<br />\n<br />\n越南雖受美國新任總統川普正式退出跨太平洋夥伴協定（TPP）影響，但川普對中國貨品課徵45%的關稅的威脅，加上越南便宜的勞動力，反而使外資對越南的投資興趣反而愈來愈大。<br />\n根據世界銀行，TPP將使越南國內生產毛額（GDP）在2030年前增加8%，尤其是越南可望成為去年對美國出口最多的東協國家。<br />\n<br />\n但美國退出TPP並未澆熄跨國企業對越南的熱情。從稻米、咖啡等農產品出口轉型為東南亞的製造業中心，越南多年來一直享受外資帶來的經濟繁榮。川普對中國的指責，以及威脅要對中國產品課徵45%的關稅，可能成為企業將製造業遷移到其他國家的動力，越南是最具吸引力的國家之一。<br />\n<br />\n越南服裝製造商NhaBe供應Calvin Klein、Michael Kors和Kenneth Cole等知名品牌的服飾。自2011年以來該公司的出口額已經翻了一倍多，去年達到7.29億美元。NhaBe負責訂單、設計和製造的總經理拉斯考（Michael Laskau）表示：「我們所有的工廠正全力運作中。我不覺得我們的客戶會離開。」<br />\n<br />\n在越南僱用4,500名員工的臺南紡織公司，透過電子郵件發表聲明說，即便TPP夭折也不會影響在當地的計劃。聲明指出，鑒於該公司的實力還有承諾，考慮在下半年在越南進一步擴張業務。<br />\n<br />\n法國投資銀行Natixis駐香港資深經濟學家阮鄭氏（Trinh Nguyen）表示，越南將繼續吸引外商直接投資勞力密集企業，以及吸引想搶占越南快速發展國內市場的投資人。<br />\n<br />\n越南外交部發言人黎海平（Le Hai Binh） 24日晚間表示，越南計劃持續改革，並將履行各項貿易協定的承諾。"},{"pid":"a8c6a9ca2e75269fa730bae4dd235d922ff1cfc6","tid":98096,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d298422e35a88c74af571d66cc85c463774bdbb","tid":98096,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"說好的中國成為最大贏家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be3418265e88fb9960ced7a90ceca749e40854a","tid":98096,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"越南大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc7f136f8100a5c3e9c3e93ae86476877d3869b","tid":98096,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"TPP又係越南或成最大贏家<br />\n退出TPP又係越南或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d3927b62e1590a463779a34ce1d3c6bfebda68","tid":98096,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>說好的中國成為最大贏家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國成為最大贏家，越南第二大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f873aff5a9b3c7b83056a5fb14cc5eecf741f46","tid":98096,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>說好的中國成為最大贏家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國成為最大贏家，越南第二大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52de2166383235490d0ba5062ff4005b416b6914","tid":98096,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"有料唔怕競爭"},{"pid":"d32d07d2da452c4d16bdd029a2d35cab42679021","tid":98096,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>說好的中國成為最大贏家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國成為最大贏家，越南第二大<img src=\"/assets/face